item.title: CVE-2024-25097|2024-03-13T15:58:36.703Z -- ThemeNcode LLC -- TNC PDF viewer
item.description: Improper Neutralization of Input During Web Page Generation ('Cross-site Scripting') vulnerability in ThemeNcode LLC TNC PDF viewer allows Stored XSS.This issue affects TNC PDF viewer: from n/a through 2.8.0.
